fields.description:
Install Specific Titanium SDK menu lists 2.0.1.GA, but it is an invalid release.

Steps to Reproduce:

1. Help > Install Specific Titanium SDK...
2. Select 2.0.1.GA.

Actual Result:

2.0.1.GA is on the list.

Expected Result:

Only 2.0.1.GA2 should be on the list, as the other release did not include the required modules.
fields.summary: Titanium Studio: Help > Install Specific Titanium SDK: 2.0.1.GA is included in the list, but it was not a valid release

comments.body:
Attaching 'sdk list.png'. This is the current Studio 3.0.0 sdk list.

Resolving ticket as Cannot Reproduce.

The unexpected behavior no longer occurs.
